```

### Examples

The following sample code shows how to decrypt a PDF file.

```csharp
[C#]
	// The path to your PDF File.
	string pdfFilePath = "YOUR_PDF_FILE_PATH";

	// Open document
	using (Document document = new Document(pdfFilePath, "YOUR_PASSWORD"))
